            <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('/health', '_blank')">â¤ï¸ å¥åº·æ£€æŸ¥</button>
            <button class="btn" onclick="toggleLogs()">ğŸ“‹ æŸ¥çœ‹æ—¥å¿—</button>
            
